articles.author: Aislinn Murphy
articles.title: Rivian, Tesla reach deal for using EV supercharger network - Fox Business
articles.description: A deal recently inked by Rivian Automotive and Tesla will open up the Elon Musk-run company's Supercharger network in North America to the EV startup.
articles.content:
Rivian Automotive and Tesla inked a deal for access to the Elon Musk-run company’s Supercharger network for electric vehicles (EVs).
